WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.010
I named a special gift Dad got for me today.

00:03.800 --> 00:04.690
I named it Lain.

00:05.520 --> 00:06.810
She’s another me.

00:07.570 --> 00:09.260
My only friend.

00:10.770 --> 00:15.040
But when I go to junior high, I’ll make real friends.

00:15.970 --> 00:20.860
If I appear at ease and lighthearted, won’t other kids like me?
